{"word":"G606 - ἀπόκειμαι - apókeimai - ap-ok'-i-mahee - Be appointed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπόκειμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apókeimai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ok'-i-mahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be appointed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வைத்திரு, நியமி"},{"paragraph":"to be laid away, laid by, reserved"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2749 - κεῖμαι - keîmai - ki'-mahee/2749\">G2749</a>; to <i>be reserved</i>; figuratively to <i>await:</i> - be appointed, (be) laid up.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1945/1945\">G1945</a>, <a href=\"#/G2621/2621\">G2621</a>, <a href=\"#/G2749/2749\">G2749</a>, <a href=\"#/G345/345\">G345</a>, <a href=\"#/G3873/3873\">G3873</a>, <a href=\"#/G4029/4029\">G4029</a>, <a href=\"#/G4295/4295\">G4295</a>, <a href=\"#/G480/480\">G480</a>, <a href=\"#/G4873/4873\">G4873</a>, <a href=\"#/G606/606\">G606</a>"}]}